<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>lmạ tlqy fy ʿyny dmʿh</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- lmạ tlqy fy ʿyny dmʿh wtlạqyny mḥtạj ạ̹lyk
 lmạ tlqy fy qlby ạnẗ wtwạsyny wạ̉nạ byn ạ̹ydyk
 (ḥḍnk ạ̹nt mrsy rwḥy )2 rwḥy dạymạ btnạdyk
 yạyswʿ
 2- lmạ tyjy ạlmwjẗ tṣnʿ jwẗ qlby kẖwf jdyd
 wạ̉lqy mwjẗ tạnyẗ tmnʿ rnẗ ạlạ̉frạḥ fy ʿyd
 (ḥḍnk ạ̹nt mrsy rwḥy )2 rwḥy dạymạ btnạdyk
 yạyswʿ</lyrics>
